  ppc stable wrt bug #525148

  04 May 2015; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> mpv-0.8.3.ebuild,
  mpv-0.9.1.ebuild, mpv-9999.ebuild:
  ebuild improvements, thanks to Nikoli and kensington

  04 May 2015; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Make my de facto primary maintainer role more explicit

  04 May 2015; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> mpv-0.9.1.ebuild,
  mpv-9999.ebuild:
  Undo regressions in formatting and ewarn/einfo messages. Undo ~hppa keywording
  of live version.

  03 May 2015; Maxim Koltsov <maksbotan@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  mpv-0.9.1.ebuild, mpv-9999.ebuild:
  Update 9999 and 0.9.1 ebuild, add drm USE flag. Thanks to Nikoli.

